			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "This AD plays during the Ketheric Showdown in the lower Colony. It will play on the first available player character.\r\n\r\n- Load SCL_Main_A\r\n- Using ReCon command \"oe KethericShowdown_Start\"  to teleport yourself there.\r\n- Go through the dialog, approach Ketheric, go through that dialog too. Combat will start.\r\n- Once the first (speaker available) player gets their turn in combat, this AD will play on them."
				},
